Usage: set_wire_load_model [-help] [<list_of_instances_or_ports>]
                           [-library <library_name>] [-max] [-min]
                           -name <wireload_model>

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
<list_of_instances_or_ports>     # List of instances or ports
                                 # (string, optional)
-library <library_name>          # Specifies the technology library to use when
                                 # searching for the wireload_model name
                                 # (string, optional)
-max                             # Sets the wireload model only for the max PVT
                                 # corner (bool, optional)
-min                             # Sets the wireload model only for the minimum
                                 # PVT corner (bool, optional)
-name <wireload_model>           # Wireload model name (string, required)